2
00:00:19,687 --> 00:00:20,895
Hey, Alfredo.

3
00:00:22,898 --> 00:00:26,025
- You done already?
- No. Not yet. I finish tomorrow.

4
00:00:26,151 --> 00:00:29,320
- Mexico playing Argentina on TV?
- No, no.

5
00:00:30,614 --> 00:00:32,490
My asthma is very bad today.

6
00:00:32,616 --> 00:00:35,451
Six years, Alfredo.
You can't lie to me.

7
00:00:35,577 --> 00:00:37,370
- I'm throwing a dinner...
- First thing tomorrow...

8
00:00:37,496 --> 00:00:38,788
Party's tonight.

9
